svg.text: THE MURDER HOUSE IS BUILT BY“SURGEON TO THE STARS” CHARLES MONTGOMERYFOR HIS WIFE NORA
DENTIST DR. CURAN RAPES AND KILLS ELIZABETH SHORT. DR.MONTGOMERY HELPS TO HIDE THE BODY.
CONSTANCE MOVES TO LOS ANGE;ESTO PURSUE AN ACTING CAREER
TATE IS BORN.TROY AND BRYAN BREAK INTO THE HOUSEAND ARE KILLED BY THE INFANTATA
CONSTANCE MOVES OUT OF THE HOUSE WITHHER CHILDREN.SAM AND NIKKI ARGENTO MOVE IN ANDGET MURDERED SHORTLY AFTER.
LARRY HARVEY AND HIS FAMILY MOVE TO THEMURDER HOUSE.CONSTANCE BEGINS AN AFFAIR WITH LARRY ANDWHEN HIS WIFE FOUND OUT, SHE SET THE HOUSE ON FIRE KILLING HERSELF AND THEIR TWO DAUGHTERS.
VIVIEN GOES INTO LABOR.SHE GIVES BIRTH TO ONE STILLBORNAND ONE HEALTHY BABY.VIVIEN AND BEN DIES.CONSTANCE TAKES THE BABY FORHERSELF.
VIVIEN MISCARRIES HER BABY.BEN GETS CAUGHT CHEATING ON VIVIEN WITH HAYDENAND THE FAMILY MOVES TO THE MURDER HOUSE
TATE GOES FOR HIS FIRST THERAPY WITH BEN.LARRY KILLS HAYDEN.
CONSTANCE MURDERS HUGO AND MOIRA IN THE HOUSE.
THE HOUSE IS BEING USED AS A SORORITY HOUSE FOR A NURSING SCHOOL. R.FRANKLINMURDERS TAKE PLACE
CHARLES AND NORA BEGIN PERFORMING ABORTIONS IN THEIR BASEMENT.ONE PATIENT’S BOYFRIEND KIDNAPS THE MONTGOMERY’S BABY AND KILLS HIM.
THIS IS A CHRONOLOGY OF EVENTS FOR THE AMERICAN HORROR STORY SEASON 1 “MURDER HOUSE”
